{"tid":1377099,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警方警方發現上環有示威者縱火 嚴厲譴責示威者一切暴力行為","createTime":"2019-07-28T13:00:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T13:07:48.000Z","uid":212626,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"37985e01b6afc60523d3fc2ea68e9993afb0cf72","tid":1377099,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:00:30.000Z","msg":"＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n電台及電視台當值宣布員注意：<br />\n<br />\n請盡快播出下列消息，並在適當時間重播：<br />\n<br />\n  警方現正（七月二十八日）在港島區西面向東進行驅散行動，示威者在多處地方縱火。其中，有人在上環西港城附近，燃燒手推車上的紙皮雜物，並將手推車推向警方防線，嚴重威脅在場人士的人身安全。<span style=\"color: red;\">示威者使用的暴力正在升級</span>。警方對示威者一切暴力行為，予以嚴厲譴責，呼籲在場人士保持冷靜。<br />\n<br />\n  警方必須指出，有關示威者正在參與未經批准的集結，觸犯香港法例。警方呼籲，在場人士立即停止衝擊警方防線或襲擊警務人員，停止一切違法行為，盡快離開現場。<br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月28日（星期日）<br />\n香港時間20時45分<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/28/P2019072800816.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.info.gov.hk%2Fgia%2Fgeneral%2F201907%2F28%2FP2019072800816.htm&d=W0WGn%2FLYmVT4dQ5oB2FXDZSOxZpZ29aBESoBY3kI%2Fuw%3D&h=0a82f1c9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.info.gov.hk/gia/general/201907/28/P2019072800816.htm</a>"},{"pid":"303cc9c41a4d7b35154c3f8a6c89c76acf5b3e7b","tid":1377099,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:00:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打多咗個警方"},{"pid":"58e10ee4d54b5e989703491482ab65fe7196b8b0","tid":1377099,"uid":231583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:02:10.000Z","msg":"狗一早就升級曬武力瘋狂掃射"},{"pid":"4e26e8d6edffe15164f7d2be74c37fca2b17f0de","tid":1377099,"uid":54946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T13:04:05.000Z","msg":"太過分啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62e91669826fbc797f1c1618a85122da27